        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="book-genre" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ahwatukee City Lifestyle &middot; August 2025</p>
          <h3>Daily Pep Talks with a Pooch</h3>
          <p>Norbert was featured on the cover of the Kids and Pets edition of Ahwatukee City Lifestyle magazine. The article tells the story of how morning pep talks with Norbert grew into storytime videos, a published children's book, and a community of over 56,000 followers united by kindness.</p>
          <a href="https://citylifestyle.com/articles/daily-pep-talks-with-a-pooch" class="btn btn--dark-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Read the Article</a>
